Instead, however, these governments committed even more debt to the state.
Other countries, apart from a few exceptions such as Hungary, Albania, Pakistan or Egypt, have managed much more rationally than our Republic.
This is a huge disgrace, which is mainly due to the previous governments.
We are among the countries that, on a global scale, are least at risk of poverty.
